{"tid":2087642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔一路話國安法好膠 習總小學雞","createTime":"2020-06-30T17:59:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T18:11:12.000Z","uid":57073,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c37b447b90d4d53395f5a97e98a8061027df460d","tid":2087642,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T17:59:34.000Z","msg":"但其實習總先係贏家<br />\n中國經濟下滑, WARS+水災, 一帶一路中國夢開始炒車<br />\n國內開始有聲音反習<br />\n<br />\n習而家根本就唔會理你國際點睇/香港點死<br />\n重點係要鞏固權力<br />\n<br />\n而家擺明車馬將所有中國嘅問題推落去外國勢力借香港港獨份子搞事<br />\n<br />\n所以中國經濟差 並唔係中國領導問題<br />\n而家外國勢力別有用心<br />\n<br />\n香港就用國安法打壓所有反對聲音<br />\n美國就Keep住煲黑人平權 夾埋民主黨拉Trump落台 成堆大公司杯葛FB IG 話Trump hate speech<br />\n<br />\n如果成功平定香港事件 習就領功<br />\n平定唔到都要美國一齊炒車<br />\n然後推晒落中美戰爭到"},{"pid":"9c80e9e94aa4715f8800fd874c690d8a24873f4e","tid":2087642,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T18:00:24.000Z","msg":"Democrat 上咪一樣"},{"pid":"d4283737ed85356aeb89825ea39981911278c81d","tid":2087642,"uid":57073,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9c80e9e94aa4715f8800fd874c690d8a24873f4e","tid":2087642,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T18:00:24.000Z","msg":"Democrat 上咪一樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T18:03:39.000Z","msg":"仲仆街過Trump<br />\n班友同CCP千斯萬縷<br />\n變返Obama咁 養大中共"},{"pid":"4e0a5f01d77037a61bad4b95d309e0ae68e192d3","tid":2087642,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d4283737ed85356aeb89825ea39981911278c81d","tid":2087642,"uid":57073,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9c80e9e94aa4715f8800fd874c690d8a24873f4e","tid":2087642,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T18:00:24.000Z","msg":"Democrat 上咪一樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T18:03:39.000Z","msg":"仲仆街過Trump<br />\n班友同CCP千斯萬縷<br />\n變返Obama咁 養大中共"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T18:04:46.000Z","msg":"唔會"},{"pid":"d4c81bb717ae33a96821c2300944793cecbc8cde","tid":2087642,"uid":266503,"like